# dns-stack.list.chroot
# DNS/DNSSEC resolver (unbound), PowerDNS authoritative server + SQLite
# backend, and Avahi mDNS daemon + discovery utilities.
#
# unbound         — recursive resolver with DNSSEC validation and DoT upstream
# pdns-server     — PowerDNS Authoritative Server (MASTER nodes only)
# pdns-backend-sqlite3 — SQLite3 storage backend for PowerDNS
# avahi-daemon    — mDNS/DNS-SD daemon for local node discovery
# avahi-utils     — avahi-browse and companion CLI tools
# libnss-mdns     — NSS plugin so getaddrinfo() resolves .local names

unbound
pdns-server
pdns-backend-sqlite3
avahi-daemon
avahi-utils
libnss-mdns
